text: James Bruce (born 17 June 1993) is a Zimbabwean cricketer. He made his first- class debut for Mid West Rhinos in the 2016–17 Logan Cup on 19 April 2017. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Zimbabwean cricketers Category:Mid West Rhinos cricketers Category:Sportspeople from Harare
